sentences: Catherina  Maria Leopoldina Cibbini-Kozeluch (Katerina Koželuh) (b. 20 February 1785, d. 12 August 1858) was an Austrian pianist and composer of Bohemian ancestry.
She was born in Vienna, the daughter of prominent composer, pianist and music publisher Leopold Kozeluch.
Cibbini-Kozeluch died in Zakupy, near Česká Lípa.
